%h1 Google Authenticator Setup

%p Follow the instructions below to set up Google Authenticator:

%ol
  %li Download and install the Google Authenticator app on your mobile device.
  %li Open the app and click the '+' button to add a new account manually.
  %li Scan the QR code below or enter the secret key manually:

#qr-code
  = image_tag @qr_code_url

%p Secret Key: #{@secret}

%p After scanning the QR code or entering the secret key, the app will display a 6-digit code. Enter the code below to complete the setup:

= form_tag verify_qr_code_path, method: :post do
  = label_tag :otp_attempt, 'Google Authenticator Code'
  = text_field_tag :otp_attempt
  = submit_tag 'Verify'
